title: Jane Seton: or, the Kings Advocate. A Scottish historical romance
author: Grant, James
snippet: On the high and rocky island, which, though it hasnow become a promontory, was then completely surrounded by the sea at high water, stood a tower belonging to the Duries of Durie.
